QSDotfiles uses code, ideas, and design patterns from the following projects:

- **caelestia-dots** by ItsABigIgloo (https://github.com/ItsABigIgloo/caelestia-sddm)
  GPL-3.0 — Quickshell shell QML, MaterialThemeLoader, ConfigLoader, overview, app search
- **JaKooLit** modular dotfiles (https://github.com/JaKooLit)
  GPL-3.0 — modular Hyprland config structure, simple-sddm-2 theme, tuned keybinds approach
- **Hyprland** (https://github.com/hyprwm/Hyprland)
  BSD-3-Clause — window manager
- **Quickshell** (https://github.com/outfoxxed/quickshell)
  LGPL-2.1 — QML shell engine
- **matugen** (https://github.com/InioX/matugen)
  MIT — Material You color generation

